## Test Commands
```bash
uv run pytest tests/unit -q
uv run pytest tests/integration -q
uv run python -m src.main --help
```

## Lint Commands
```bash
uv run ruff check .          # Python linting (ruff>=0.9 configured in pyproject.toml)
cd frontend && pnpm lint     # ESLint
cd frontend && pnpm typecheck  # TypeScript type check
```

When adding a new phase, update all phase-order surfaces together:
`src/orchestration/workflow.py`, `src/orchestration/resume.py`,
`src/web/app.py`, and `frontend/src/lib/constants.ts`.
In `frontend/src/lib/constants.ts`, update both the display `PHASE_ORDER`
and the resume-only `RESUME_PHASE_ORDER` when backend `PHASE_ORDER` changes.
